{"mappings":"AAAA;;;;AAIA;;;;;;AAOA;;;;;;;;AAQA;EACE;;;;;;AAMF;;;;;AAKA;;;;AAIA;;;;;;AAOA;;;;;AAKA;EACE","sources":["src/css/features.css"],"sourcesContent":[".features--section {\r\n  margin-top: calc(var(--index) * 12);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.features--section .features {\r\n  display: grid;\r\n  /* grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(15rem, 1fr)); */\r\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n  gap: 1rem;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.features--section .features__feature {\r\n  padding: calc(var(--index) * 1.2);\r\n  background-color: var(--color-accent--lightest);\r\n  border: 1px solid var(--color-grey);\r\n  border-radius: var(--border-radius);\r\n  transition: all 300ms ease-in-out;\r\n}\r\n\r\n@media (max-width: 600px) {\r\n  .features--section .features {\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\r\n    gap: 1rem;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n.features--section .features__feature:hover,\r\n.features--section .features__feature:focus {\r\n  transform: scale(1.1);\r\n  box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\r\n}\r\n.features--section .icon-box {\r\n  margin-bottom: 2rem;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.features--section .feature-icon {\r\n  width: 3rem;\r\n  height: 3rem;\r\n  filter: saturate(100%) invert(35%) sepia(50%) hue-rotate(115deg)\r\n    saturate(500%) contrast(100%);\r\n}\r\n\r\n.features--section .feature--title {\r\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\r\n  letter-spacing: 0.1rem;\r\n}\r\n\r\n@media (max-width: 600px) {\r\n  .features--section .feature--description {\r\n    font-size: calc(var(--index) * 1.2);\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n"],"names":[],"version":3,"file":"index.75b99cb1.css.map","sourceRoot":"/__parcel_source_root/"}